<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:15:47 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在反对派抗议中，尼泊尔总理赢得议会信任投票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/amid-opposition-protests-nepal-pm-wins-parliamentary-vote-confidence-2024-05-20/</link><description>尼泊尔总理周一赢得议会信任投票，反对派抗议要求议会对其内政部长在从政前非法收受多家公司资金的指控进行调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:08:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/amid-opposition-protests-nepal-pm-wins-parliamentary-vote-confidence-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>彭博社报道，中国监管机构计划召开欧洲投资者会议以重振股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulators-plan-european-investor-meet-revive-stocks-bloomberg-reports-2024-05-20/</link><description>彭博社周一援引不愿透露姓名的知情人士的话报道称，中国市场监管机构计划本周与欧洲投资者举行会议，以重振他们对全球第二大股市的兴趣。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:07:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulators-plan-european-investor-meet-revive-stocks-bloomberg-reports-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>台湾新总统就任后台中关系的关键事实</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/key-facts-taiwan-china-relations-new-taiwan-president-takes-office-2024-05-20/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德在一月份赢得选举后于周一就职。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 06:34:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/key-facts-taiwan-china-relations-new-taiwan-president-takes-office-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>独家：特斯拉采取损害控制措施，为欧洲车队买家提供折扣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-doing-damage-control-discounts-european-fleet-buyers-2024-05-20/</link><description>特斯拉正在努力安抚一些欧洲租赁公司，因为该汽车制造商一再下调零售价格，导致其车队的价值大幅下降，而且其缓慢的服务和昂贵的维修疏远了他们的企业客户。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 05:03:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-doing-damage-control-discounts-european-fleet-buyers-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾敦促中国允许对有争议的南海浅滩进行审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-should-allow-scrutiny-disputed-shoal-2024-05-20/</link><description>在指责北京破坏黄岩岛海洋环境后，菲律宾周一挑战中国开放黄岩岛接受国际监督。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 03:03:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-should-allow-scrutiny-disputed-shoal-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国商务部禁止部分美国企业从事进出口活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-commerce-ministry-bans-some-us-firms-import-export-activities-2024-05-20/</link><description>中国商务部周一表示，将禁止部分美国企业从事与中国相关的进出口活动，包括向台湾出售武器，并禁止它们在中国进行新的投资。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 02:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-commerce-ministry-bans-some-us-firms-import-export-activities-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国的房地产支持措施令人失望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/most-chinese-developers-shares-fall-despite-latest-support-measures-2024-05-20/</link><description>中国开发商的股价周一出现波动，原因是投资者担心中国为稳定受危机打击的房地产行业而采取的“历史性”举措未能达到促进需求和信心可持续好转所需的水平。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 02:29:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/most-chinese-developers-shares-fall-despite-latest-support-measures-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>投资者等待美联储更多指引，美元保持稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-await-clues-us-rate-path-2024-05-20/</link><description>美元周一基本稳定，尽管通胀显示出降温迹象，但在美联储官员发表谨慎言论后，投资者等待进一步线索来帮助绘制美国利率走势。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 01:19:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-await-clues-us-rate-path-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>赖清德宣誓就任台湾新总统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/lai-ching-te-sworn-taiwans-new-president-2024-05-20/</link><description>总统府电视直播的画面显示，赖清德周一宣誓就任台湾新总统。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 01:09:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/lai-ching-te-sworn-taiwans-new-president-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>降息预期坚定，金属、股市飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-20/</link><description>周一，亚洲股市触及两年高位，而铜和黄金周一创下历史新高，因投资者押注降息即将到来，以及中国加大力度稳定陷入困境的房地产行业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 00:53:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>日经新闻报道，日本和东盟计划制定汽车生产联合战略</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/japan-asean-plan-joint-strategy-auto-production-nikkei-reports-2024-05-19/</link><description>据《日经新闻》周一报道，日本和东南亚国家联盟（东盟）计划在东南亚集团内制定首个汽车生产和销售联合战略，以应对中国在电动汽车市场日益增长的影响力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 22:48:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/japan-asean-plan-joint-strategy-auto-production-nikkei-reports-2024-05-19/</guid></item><item><title>台湾新总统呼吁中国停止威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-taiwan-president-take-office-facing-angry-china-2024-05-19/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周一要求中国停止军事和政治威胁，并在就职演说中表示，和平是唯一的选择，北京必须尊重台湾人民的选择。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 22:09:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-taiwan-president-take-office-facing-angry-china-2024-05-19/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：中国阴云笼罩市场情绪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-19/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 21:48:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-19/</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利多瑙河船只相撞，两人死亡五人失踪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/two-dead-five-missing-after-suspected-boat-collision-danube-2024-05-19/</link><description>匈牙利警方周日表示，周六晚间，一艘小型摩托艇在布达佩斯以北的多瑙河上与一艘游轮相撞，造成两人死亡、五人失踪。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 10:06:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/two-dead-five-missing-after-suspected-boat-collision-danube-2024-05-19/</guid></item><item><title>英国首相沙普斯表示，中俄关系的加强威胁着民主</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/britains-shapps-says-stronger-china-russia-ties-threaten-democracy-2024-05-19/</link><description>英国国防部长格兰特·沙普斯周日表示，他对中国国家主席习近平和俄罗斯总统普京最近加强外交关系感到非常担忧，称这对民主构成了威胁。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 08:28:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/britains-shapps-says-stronger-china-russia-ties-threaten-democracy-2024-05-19/</guid></item></channel></rss>